channel.title: Photoshop CS6
channel.description: Hey guys, my photoshop recently crashed somehow and now won't work so I had to uninstall it and I downloaded it again. I can't find another serial number that works for this. Every site I go to try's to make me download some file and most of them are viruses. Does anybody have a CS6 License Key they can comment or pm me?

item.title: Photoshop CS6
item.dc:creator: @xx_matty_xx Justin Bieber
item.description:
@xx_matty_xx wrote:

You need to checkout and when it asks for something called a “Card Number” you need to find a credit card (any, it doesn’t matter), enter the 16 digits on the front and then the last 3 digits on the back. Click checkout and the key will appear in your email inbox.
